  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0daf\u0db8\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A millionaire has been killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kandy Headquarters Police say that a 65-year-old millionaire woman who lived alone in a large house near Ratu Bokku Junction in Lake Waya Raum, Kandy, was hacked to death.",
        "The police say that a woman named Kamani Ranasinghe (65) has been killed in this way.",
        "The police mention that the woman has retired from an executive grade job in the government and is living alone and has rented out a large number of shops near the large house.",
        "The police investigation also revealed that the woman's husband had died earlier and their two children were living in Australia.",
        "An eyewitness who did not wish to be named said that he saw a black man about five feet tall come out of the house where the woman lived with a knife in his hand and his hand was cut and bleeding.",
        "The spokesman said that he did not go near him as the man threatened him with a knife and then went inside the house and said that the woman was on the ground and was struggling.",
        "He said that since she died shortly after that, he did not take steps to hospitalize her and he said that he informed the police about it.",
        "The police suspect that the murder has taken place over a property issue, and further police investigation is being carried out through several stages."
      ],
